text.paragraph:
Safe use of Methocarbamol Tablets has not been established with regard to possible adverse effects upon fetal development.  There have been reports of fetal and congential abnormalities following in utero exposure to methocarbamol.  Therefore, Methocarbamol Tablets should not be used in women who are or may become pregnant and particularly during early pregnancy unless in the judgment of the physician the potential benefits outweigh the possible hazards (see 
                                          WARNINGS
                                       ).
